### Login
- POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/v1/users/login
- **Description**: Authenticate a user.
- **Request Body**:
    ```json
    {
        "email": "jcole@gmail.come",
        "password": "su@glu"
    }
    ```
- **Response**:
